Package org.neo4j.graphdb.factory.module

Class GlobalModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.graphdb.factory.module.GlobalModule
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestDatabaseManagementServiceFactory.TestDatabaseGlobalModule
    public class GlobalModule
extends Object
    Global module for DatabaseManagementServiceFactory. This creates all global services and components from DBMS.
